c/6776865ab0b7d061dcd4ae27919db0a4/799d3/screenshot.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6776865ab0b7d061dcd4ae27919db0a4/00d96/screenshot.png 148w,\n/static/6776865ab0b7d061dcd4ae27919db0a4/0b23c/screenshot.png 295w,\n/static/6776865ab0b7d061dcd4ae27919db0a4/799d3/screenshot.png 590w,\n/static/6776865ab0b7d061dcd4ae27919db0a4/2a3d6/screenshot.png 885w,\n/static/6776865ab0b7d061dcd4ae27919db0a4/ae92f/screenshot.png 1180w,\n/static/6776865ab0b7d061dcd4ae27919db0a4/c72b4/screenshot.png 2114w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>게시물에 하단에는 게시물을 소셜 공유 할 수 있는 버튼들이 위치합니다.<br>\n그 아래로는 광고와 댓글이 위치합니다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"시리즈-게시물\"><a href=\"#%EC%8B%9C%EB%A6%AC%EC%A6%88-%EA%B2%8C%EC%8B%9C%EB%AC%BC\" aria-label=\"시리즈 게시물 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>시리즈 게시물</h4>\n<p>만약 시리즈 게시물이라면 위와 같이 게시물 상단에 시리즈 목록이 표시됩니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c476d2829cc06a41a5486bda04fcf1df/c4d01/DraggedImage-4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.91836734693878%; position: relative; bottom: 